<body>
<section name="@Springfield">
	<p>
		POJO Class 에   @Springfield 을 선언하면  Generic 류의 Controller / Service / Repository Bean 을 
		 생성하여 CoC 에 의해 "~Controller", "~Validator", "~Service", "~Repository" 라는 Bean Name 으로, 
		 springframework 의 applicationContext에 등록 한다. 
	</p>
	<p>
		<img/>
	</p>
	<p>
		자동 생성, 등록 되는 Bean 종류 및 구현체는 strategy 속성 값에 따라 결정된다. 
	</p>
	<table border="1">
		<tr><th>Springfield Strategy</th>	<th>bean name  </th>	<th>bean type</th>	<th>bean implement</th></tr>
		<tr><td rowspan="4"><b>SQLSESSION</b></td><td>"~Controller"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityController<T,Q>]]></i></td> <td>com.u2ware.springfield.controller. EntityHandler</td></tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Validator"</td> <td><i><![CDATA[EntityValidator<T,Q>]]></i></td>  <td>com.u2ware.springfield.validation. EntityValidatorImpl</td></tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Service"</td>   <td><i><![CDATA[EntityService<T,Q>]]></i></td>	  <td>com.u2ware.springfield.service. EntityServiceImpl</td></tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Repository"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityRepository<T,ID>]]></i></td><td><b>com.u2ware.springfield.repository.sqlsession. EntitySqlsessionRepository</b></td></tr>
		<tr><td rowspan="4"><b>JPA</b></td>       <td>"~Controller"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityController<T,Q>]]></i></td> <td>com.u2ware.springfield.controller. EntityHandler</td></tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Validator"</td> <td><i><![CDATA[EntityValidator<T,Q>]]></i></td>  <td>com.u2ware.springfield.validation. EntityValidatorImpl</td></tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Service"</td>   <td><i><![CDATA[EntityService<T,Q>]]></i></td>    <td>com.u2ware.springfield.service. EntityServiceImpl</td></tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Repository"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityRepository<T,ID>]]></i></td><td><b>com.u2ware.springfield.repository.jpa. EntityJpaRepository</b></td></tr>
		<tr><td rowspan="4"><b>MONGODB</b></td>   <td>"~Controller"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityController<T,Q>]]></i></td> <td>com.u2ware.springfield.controller. EntityHandler</td>	</tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Validator"</td> <td><i><![CDATA[EntityValidator<T,Q>]]></i></td>  <td>com.u2ware.springfield.validation. EntityValidatorImpl</td>	</tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Service"</td>   <td><i><![CDATA[EntityService<T,Q>]]></i></td>    <td>com.u2ware.springfield.service. EntityServiceImpl</td>	</tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Repository"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityRepository<T,ID>]]></i></td><td><b>com.u2ware.springfield.repository.mongodb. EntityMongodbRepository</b></td></tr>
		<tr><td rowspan="3"><b>DTO</b></td>       <td>"~Controller"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityController<T,Q>]]></i></td> <td>com.u2ware.springfield.controller. EntityHandler</td>	</tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Validator"</td> <td><i><![CDATA[EntityValidator<T,Q>]]></i></td>  <td>com.u2ware.springfield.validation. EntityValidatorImpl</td>	</tr>
		<tr>                                      <td>"~Service"</td>   <td><i><![CDATA[EntityService<T,Q>]]></i></td>    <td>com.u2ware.springfield.service. EntityServiceImpl</td>	</tr>
		<tr><td><b>SQLSESSION _REPOSITORY_ONLY</b></td><td>"~Repository"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityRepository<T,ID>]]></i></td><td><b>com.u2ware.springfield.repository.sqlsession. EntitySqlsessionRepository</b></td></tr>
		<tr><td><b>JPA _REPOSITORY_ONLY</b>       </td><td>"~Repository"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityRepository<T,ID>]]></i></td><td><b>com.u2ware.springfield.repository.jpa. EntityJpaRepository</b></td></tr>
		<tr><td><b>MONGODB _REPOSITORY_ONLY</b>   </td><td>"~Repository"</td><td><i><![CDATA[EntityRepository<T,ID>]]></i></td><td><b>com.u2ware.springfield.repository.mongodb. EntityMongodbRepository</b></td></tr>
	</table>
	
</section>


